nodes.text: In 14 ABY, the criminal Lannik Racto had an office at the upper levels of a large building on Coruscant. There, he was captured by Jedi Jaden Korr. Once Jaden got to the top, Racto taunted the Jedi and opened a door with a room full of assassin droids. Racto then caged himself in a giant metal box which was opened later.
